name: RSTimber Traders
tag_list: construction-machinery, scaffolding-product, prop-jack, metal-coupler, scaffolding-material, wooden-ply, construction-channel, slotted-angle-plate-and-steel-construction-plate-
overview:
Established in the year 1989, at Delhi (India), we, “RS Timber Traders”, are one of the leading names, engaged in Manufacturing, Trading, Supplying and Exporting comprehensive assortment of Construction Machinery, Scaffolding Product, Prop Jack, Metal Coupler, Scaffolding Material, Wooden Ply, Construction Channel, Slotted Angle Plate and Steel Construction Plate. The products we are offering to our prestigious customers are procured from the certified and trusted vendors of the market.

Infrastructure: The company has constructed a well furnished infrastructure that is furnished with state of the art machinery. We have all kinds of advanced technological tools to meet the production requirements. With the same, we properly ensure the perfect polishing and finishing of the goods available with us as such as Teak Round logs, Gmelina Wood logs, etc.

Vendor Base: With rich vendor base, we are engaged in exporting and supplying high quality products. Our vendors enable us to carry out hassle-free orders delivery. We are associated with the reputed vendors on the basis of their trust and credibility, as they play a crucial role in the success of our organization.

Our Team: Supported by an adroit team of professionals, our organization has been able to establish a remarkable position in the industry. We have a well integrated team of administrators and workers, which is well versed with all the aspect of production and distribution of Logs and woods.

Our Products: Construction Machinery, Scaffolding Product, Prop Jack, Metal Coupler, Scaffolding Material, Wooden Ply, Construction Channel, Slotted Angle Plate and Steel Construction Plate.
